oai_dc:dc.dc:title: 1955 Central High School Baseball Team
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The 1955 Central High School baseball team and starting lineup. The school was established in 1917 at 161 Rains Avenue at the corner of Wedgewood Avenue. Central High School was closed in 1971 and the building demolished in 1973. 8 x 10 in.
